           SHORT='Install functions and selected system scripts then sets runlevels and  priorities.'
cat << EOF
Installs and sets runlevel priority on basic system init scripts, such as localtime.sh, mount.sh and  mountnfs.sh.
It includes functions script modified from LFS-3.1. Originally rewritten by Gerard Beekmans - gerard@linuxfromscratch.org, with code based on Matthias Benkmanns simpleinit-msb http://winterdrache.de/linux/newboot/index.html. Modified for SourceMage GNU linux.
